  "analysis": "The image exists at /app/isos/win311.img (256 MB). nginx is installed, but no QEMU binaries are in PATH and qemu-img/qemu-system did not respond. The next required step is to determine whether QEMU is installed elsewhere or must be installed. I also need to inspect the image type and package availability, and check for noVNC/websockify because nginx on port 80 should provide remote web access to VNC.",
